[[!meta date="Mon, 3 Sep 2018 17:25:18 +0000"]]
[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 3.8"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 3.8 are now fixed in Tails 3.9.

We **strongly** encourage you to
[[upgrade to Tails 3.9|news/version_3.9]] as soon as possible.

 - Tor Browser: [[!mfsa2018 22]]
 - Thunderbird: [[!mfsa2018 22]]
 - lcms2: [[!debsa2018 4284]]
 - curl: [[!debsa2018 4286]]
 - ghostscript: [[!debsa2018 4288]], [[!debsa2018 4294]]
 - texlive-bin: [[!debsa2018 4299]]
 - python2.7: [[!debsa2018 4306]]
 - python3.5: [[!debsa2018 4307]]

